languages.text: "Я виновен во многом, но не в этом. Я ничего у тебя не крал, мой технобрат. В отличие от... многих иных, кто и впрямь ограбил тебя".
"I am guilty of many things, but not the transgression you speak of. I have stolen nothing from you, my tech-comrade. Unlike... many others who have indeed robbed you."

languages.text: 「私は多くの罪を侵した。しかし、あなたの言う破戒ではない。私はあなたからなにも奪ってはいない、技術同胞よ。あなたから奪ってきた多くの他の者とは…違うのだ」
languages.original_text: "I am guilty of many things, but not the transgression you speak of. I have stolen nothing from you, my tech-comrade. Unlike... many others who have indeed robbed you."

traits.speaker: PasqalQuest_Dements

languages.text: “我确实犯下过很多罪行，但我并没有盗用过身份。我从来没有盗窃过你的东西，我的技术兄弟。我可不像……很多其他人，那些人确实抢走过本属于你的东西。”
languages.original_text: "I am guilty of many things, but not the transgression you speak of. I have stolen nothing from you, my tech-comrade. Unlike... many others who have indeed robbed you."

languages.text: "Ich habe mich vieler Dinge schuldig gemacht, aber nicht des Vergehens, von dem Ihr sprecht. Ich habe Euch nichts gestohlen, mein Techkamerad. Anders als ... viele andere, die Euch tatsächlich beraubt haben."
languages.original_text: "I am guilty of many things, but not the transgression you speak of. I have stolen nothing from you, my tech-comrade. Unlike... many others who have indeed robbed you."

languages.text: « Je suis coupable de nombreux crimes, mais pas de celui dont vous m'accusez. Je ne vous ai rien dérobé, technoconfrère. Contrairement à... bien d'autres qui vous ont effectivement volé. »
languages.original_text: "I am guilty of many things, but not the transgression you speak of. I have stolen nothing from you, my tech-comrade. Unlike... many others who have indeed robbed you."

languages.text: «Soy culpable de muchas cosas, pero no de la transgresión que insinúa. No le he robado nada, tecnocamarada. A diferencia de... muchos otros que sí le han expoliado a base de bien».

languages.text: "Birçok konuda suçu olabilirim, sözünü ettiğin konudaysa değilim. Birçoklarının aksine senden hiçbir şey çalmadım tekno yoldaşım."
languages.original_text: "I am guilty of many things, but not the transgression you speak of. I have stolen nothing from you, my tech-comrade. Unlike... many others who have indeed robbed you."

traits.locale_text: "Birçok konuda suçluyumdur ancak sözünü ettiğin konuda değil. Senden hiçbir şey çalmadım tekno yoldaşım. Senden bazı şeyler çalmış olan birçoklarının aksine."
traits.speaker: PasqalQuest_Dements
